Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.94,0:00:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}不是那裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.90,0:00:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}哈哈 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我手滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.88,0:01:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}妳沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.70,0:01:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}謝謝...妳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}妳氣的狀況越來越好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}這是修練的成果吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}真努力!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.74,0:01:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}說起來那幾位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.16,0:01:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}不知道有沒有持續的在做氣的修練呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}對了 小景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.92,0:01:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}想不想去見一下有趣的傢伙呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.18,0:01:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(960,984)}百花繚亂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.24,0:01:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}武士後談
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.40,0:01:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}來~啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}等...給我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}十兵衛 妳怎麼突然這樣啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.62,0:01:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}因為我是哥哥的劍妃啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}雖...雖是這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.30,0:01:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}所以說我就是哥哥的新娘 對吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.08,0:01:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}新娘就會'啊~'的餵他吃飯哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.96,0:01:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}來~啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:01:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.92,0:02:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}妳擅自在說什麼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}劍妃跟新娘不一樣的!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}說得沒錯!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}劍妃是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}為了幫主將戰鬥的劍姬中的力量結晶!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}和新娘是不一樣的!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}十兵衛沒辦法成為哥哥的新娘嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}啊...那個嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.22,0:02:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}雖然不是說不能...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}應該說還太早了... 不對啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}如果選新娘感到困擾的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.22,0:02:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}先選情人也可以哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}義仙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}真討厭 妳只要一出現事情就會變得更複雜... 給我閃邊去!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}再說 十兵衛 妳完全不懂對新娘的要求有多高吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.82,0:02:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}喂!專心聽我說話啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}真是的 如果要成為新娘的話就要抱持應有的覺悟哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}這是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}以我來說 這種程度我早就有所覺悟了呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:02:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}真不愧是姬大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.26,0:03:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}所謂得劍姬就是在各種情況都要處變不驚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}對妾身來說成為新娘的時代早就在意料之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}真是太厲害了 幸村大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}和某個自稱愛的戰士不一樣 有著非常強大的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}妳在說誰啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}和那個只有愛的腦殘人可不是同一個檔次呢!姬大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}妳說什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我也是 為了讓殿下說"成為我的新娘吧" 所以我無時無刻都在準備呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}這個意思不一樣吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}無視她就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}殿下三個多月就要換一次新娘 可是非常辛苦的!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}大家快趴下!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}到底是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}她可不是一般人 大家小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}的確是一群有趣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}難道 妳是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}上杉景勝大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}豬排大人?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}看來還有持續的在做氣的修練嘛!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}妳是...前田慶次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}唷 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我重新自我介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我是會津中將上杉景勝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}今後請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我是柳生道場的柳生宗朗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}好久不見了 上杉景勝大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}兼續...妳認識景勝小姐嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}景勝大人以前在我還在米澤分校時 一直對我很溫柔的恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}是一位有主家血脈的重要核心人物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}原來妳也會認識這樣的人物啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:05:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}會把便當的菜分給我 還會借我熱褲穿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}是位非常溫柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}那都是過去的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我也不是很關照過妳嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}約我去野餐卻放我鴿子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}把我帶去釣魚卻忘了我被水沖走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}在遊戲大會裡還要強迫我接受懲罰的這些事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}妳還敢叫關照我!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我忘記了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}太無恥了 稍微學習一下景勝大人的謙虛吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}這句很適合妳哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}去死死算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}那...今天來這有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我是來見你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}妳..妳在說什麼啊? 慶次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}怎麼了? 臉好紅哦 宗朗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}慶次...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}對了 前田小姐也是為了當哥哥的新娘而來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}新娘?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}是啊 十兵衛已經成為劍妃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}接下來要成為哥哥的新娘哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:05:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}妳不可能啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}新娘就必須要有領導力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}能做到的只有我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}妳在說什麼 新娘需要的是經營管理的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}從古至今都沒有餓肚子的軍隊能打勝仗的 只有能夠管理軍費的我才能勝任
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}新娘最重要的當然是愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}沒有愛的話三個月就會被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}妳的話三天都撐不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}能撐三分鐘就很扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.77,0:06:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}大家稍微停一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}一下子說新娘新娘什麼的...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}原來如此 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}依我來看 能解決目前這個問題的方法只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}就是新娘總選舉啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}新娘總選舉?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}對 大家都有當新娘的自信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}但是你卻沒做出選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}那...個...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}所以...只好由第三者來決定不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:06:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}摩天輪?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}把妳們自己的新娘介紹傳到電腦上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}讓大家來投票選出誰最適合當新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}原來如此 就是說把妾身的新娘能力讓大家見識一下嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}真有趣 就讓大家跪倒在我天生的新娘能力下吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}作為愛的戰士的我絕對不會輸!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}十兵衛也想坐摩天輪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}就這樣決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}那麼 妳們倆要怎麼辦呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.62,0:07:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}義仙我做情婦就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}男士需要女性的理由 除了繁衍之外就是發洩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}妳們兩位不這麼想嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我...我不懂妳在說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我...我只想保護幸村大人就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}半藏 我們快點去準備吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}又兵衛 我們也不能輸她們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}慶次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}宗朗 那個可是男人啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}哥哥 我們一起去坐摩天輪吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}摩天輪 摩天輪 摩天輪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}妳到底在想什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}想什麼? 宗朗他是特別的!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}妳竟然說特別的!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.65,0:08:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}前田小姐也要參加候補新娘吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}大家一起來參加才會比較有趣哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}嗯...我想想...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}好!我也來參加候補新娘!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}慶次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}宗朗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我的四十八寢技
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}成為你的新娘後我全部想來試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}等...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}不要那麼開心啦!我會害羞的!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}景勝也要...參加候補新娘!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我不會把慶次交給你的!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}什麼!景勝大人也要參加!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我要參加!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}豬排大人也要參加啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}雖然景勝大人有恩於我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}但是一碼歸一碼 我不會手下留情的!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}好 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}景勝竟然要參加那我就棄權
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}仔細想想也要有人來當選舉管理者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}只好由發起者的我來當吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我很期待景勝的新娘表現哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}慶次 妳這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.30,0:09:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}嘿嘿 現在可不能反悔哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}候選人的新娘表現是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}將透過內置在宗朗隱形眼鏡裡的攝影鏡頭進行拍攝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}然後傳輸到學校的電腦裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}還有道場和其他地方安裝的攝影鏡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.07,0:09:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}也會從各個角度拍出新娘的自我表現
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}如果覺得哪個新娘好的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}擁有選舉權的武應學園中的學生可以上面點個讚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}票數最多的人就是新娘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}選舉期間一個禮拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.57,0:10:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}好了 會有怎樣的自我表現 真讓人期待啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}第一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(1116,670)}內褲已脫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(1164,678)}就等這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(584,706)}這才是正統派
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我們是風紀委員 只要被集體召集
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我們一定會聚集到姬大人的身邊 鞠躬盡瘁死而後已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}好 那麼現在進行當時的特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}先從打掃開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}半藏 這邊的地板還是髒的!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}是 現在來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}腰部在用力一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}姬大人 謝謝您的指導
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}新娘就是大家的領導 要有管理傭人的魄力才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:11:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}怎樣 這就是我的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(524,982)}這是我們業界的獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(1436,758)}太讓人羨慕\N太不像話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(440,974)}半藏該換人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}說到新娘的話就是維持家計的財務大臣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}以毫不浪費的籌劃在背後支撐丈夫的賢內助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}幸村大人 這個月的電費漲了 這該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}好 快到夏季了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}那就穿少一點 穿學校泳裝!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.65,0:11:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}以後就穿泳裝了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}是!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}這樣電費就少30%
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}真不愧是幸村大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(1216,686)}幸村碳想舔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(568,702)}貧乳就是正義
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(1524,718)}合法蘿莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.37,0:11:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}哥~哥~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}今天天氣那麼好 一起去散步吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}十兵衛 不要靠那麼近啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我知道了!我們一起去散步!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(472,782)}萌死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(956,1022)}妹妹真可愛妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}為什麼十兵衛的票數比我漲得還快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}十兵衛不是什麼都沒表現出來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}做得挺不錯的嘛!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}肚子好餓~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}啊 兼續 妳這身打扮是怎樣啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}接下來由景勝大人和我為您做蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(1176,710)}續續來啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}給我加上"小姐"啊! 大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(524,734)}這才是正統派
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}真不愧是續續真會耍小聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}真的穿成這樣就好了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}很適合妳哦 景勝大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}是...是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我找到了呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}不讓景勝大人蒙羞 還能讓我獲勝的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}大研究 變成料理得心應手的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}和最喜歡的他心靈相通
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}讓身體變得漂亮又性感的食譜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(1292,110)}用裸體圍裙攻陷男人的心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}就是這個啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}會料理的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}既能表現出新娘的一面 又不會讓景勝大人下不了台
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}這可是完美個作戰啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}兼續 我要做什麼好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:13:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我想想 那麼可以用那個攪拌一下奶油嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.48,0:13:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}快停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}沒事啊 景勝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}宗朗 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}不...
