Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}沒...沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(1112,1026)}已保存
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(1220,782)}內褲已脫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}景勝大人 我來幫您擦...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}怎麼了? 兼續
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(1580,706)}好臀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(536,946)}屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(1676,690)}美臀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}小景 還挺厲害的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}沒想到會來這招
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}不管是誰都不懂新娘的真諦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}如果這樣就只好出奇招了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}嚴禁霸王硬上弓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.42,0:13:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}啊 宗朗 那邊不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:14:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}那邊還很髒 所以現在開始要打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}姬大人 我提水過來...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}姬大人真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}討厭 害我濕了呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我們還要更加省電才行!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}這樣就能省下70%的電費了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}也準備了宗朗的份哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}不需要!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}哥哥臉上有飯粒 十兵衛幫你拿下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}沒事吧 十...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}對...對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}真是的 看來大家都用卑鄙的手段了呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}十兵衛什麼都不知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}想裝傻也沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}這樣的話就讓你們見識一下我真正的絕技!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}金剛峰樓閣一切瑜伽瑜祇經愛染大明王的說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}運用氣力啊 兼續 好厲害哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.65,0:15:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我現在是愛即正義的劍姬 魔法少女續續小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}續續小姐 妳現在是裸體哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:15:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}太下流啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.14,0:16:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}景勝該怎麼辦才好...
