Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}對了 小景
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我現在很高興哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}因為這次的總選舉 讓大家看到了我家小景的魅力啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}應該讓大家看到妳更多的新娘表現啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}但是...就算贏了...也無法成為慶次的新娘...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}成為誰的新娘...一點也不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}沒關係 不會對妳做壞事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我的夢想是...將來和小景一起生很多活潑的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}然後湊出一支足球隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}討..討厭啦!慶次 生不了那麼多的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}沒關係 一半由我來生 就好啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}景勝會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}第三天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}第四天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}第五天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}第六天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}這真是太有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}真是有夠難纏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.88,0:18:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}現在才要開始呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}最後一定是愛會贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}一口氣戰到底
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}最終日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}宗朗 我來幫你刷背
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}不 由妾身來幫你刷背
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}不不 就讓我來幫你刷背
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}十兵衛也要!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}妳們真夠礙事的!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}景勝也來幫你刷...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:18:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}好...好難過...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}對不起 宗朗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.08,0:19:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}這樣的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}平...平常有這種服務可以很稀少的哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}宗朗 感覺怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}才不會輸妳呢!這樣如何!如何!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}妳那種飛機場是不行的!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}妳自己也大不到哪裡去啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}必殺!胸部攻擊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}姬大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}幸村大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.71,0:19:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}兩位小姐請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}這場戰鬥是她們各自必須跨越的試煉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}所以妳們不要插手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}比起這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}要不要在詳細了解一下...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}關於如何成為默默支持主人的情人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我...只要不妨礙姬大人的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}現在過去的話...也只會妨礙到幸村大人的...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}宗朗 讓我來把你洗更乾淨點!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}這就交給妾身吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}才不會輸妳們的!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}好癢哦!哥哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}對不起 十兵衛 我不是故意...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}對正室夫人無法做的事情 向情人要求的話 無論是什麼我們都必須接受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}情人最重要的就是讓主人變"大"站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}讓主人...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}站起來!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}那裡不行 快過來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}快過來這裡!宗朗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.65,0:20:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}你敢偷跑的話我絕不會原諒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.45,0:20:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我不會輸的!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}哥哥你沒事吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}宗朗 看看妳們做的好事!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}妳在胡說什麼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}不是妳的錯嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.02,0:20:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我要報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}怎樣!想打架嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}來決鬥吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我接受這場決鬥!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.11,0:20:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}戰爭啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}宗朗不會讓給你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,0:21:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我絕不可能輸給妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}這句話我原封不動的還給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}讓妳們見識一下 景勝的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.91,0:21:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.91,0:21:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}大家快住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}宗朗...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.82,0:21:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}用...用這種方式來選新娘...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}果然很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.65,0:21:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}哥哥...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.28,0:21:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}妳們快回想起來...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.11,0:21:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}十兵衛變劍妃的時候...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.74,0:21:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}我們...大家的心不是融為一體嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.71,0:21:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}那為什麼...要為了這種事...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}新娘...不是由別人決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.45,0:22:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}這麼重要的事 應該要我們大家花時間來決定的吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.77,0:22:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}正是如此 說得真好!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.54,0:22:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}慶次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}宗朗 你說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.11,0:22:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}新娘不是由投票出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.17,0:22:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}但是這不是慶次提案的...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.45,0:22:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}這次還真是不錯的消遣呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.77,0:22:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}消遣...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.77,0:22:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}是這樣嗎?慶次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.80,0:22:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}是啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.05,0:22:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}這樣就可以看到小景煩惱的樣子時..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.14,0:22:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}可說是幸運級的消遣啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.28,0:22:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}妳到底在想什麼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.77,0:22:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}給我下來 我要一拳揍飛妳!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.74,0:22:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}天啊 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.37,0:22:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}事情結束了就差不多該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.60,0:22:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}小景 快去穿好衣服我們回家了!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.40,0:22:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}那打擾妳們了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:22:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}這是什麼情況啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.80,0:22:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(980,226)}鬧劇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:22:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(1304,614)}開什麼玩笑啊啊啊啊啊!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:22:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(1248,830)}前田慶次妳太小看人啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.40,0:22:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(1688,698)}真的假的!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.82,0:22:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(608,738)}...妳...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.82,0:22:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(808,942)}....說什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:22:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}{\pos(1168,1058)}鬧...鬧劇...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}不要那些麻煩的事 當個情婦好像比較輕鬆呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.71,0:24:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}妳覺得怎樣?那個叫柳生宗朗的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.37,0:24:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}的確是個有趣的男人...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.34,0:24:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}但慶次..也太欺負人了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.37,0:24:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}抱歉抱歉 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.20,0:24:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}回到米澤後我會好好的疼愛妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.28,0:24:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}妳就原諒我吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.57,0:24:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}真是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.71,0:24:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}慶次妳...這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.00,0:24:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}武士總選舉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.60,0:24:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,fx,{\blur10}完
